it easily outshines car headlights and standard ‚Äútactical‚Äù flashlights.\nIt‚Äôs constructed from grade-5 titanium and aircraft-grade aluminum, the same materials used in modern fighter jets. That means VitalTac‚Ñ¢ is virtually indestructible.\nIt‚Äôs waterproof, resistant to freezing temperatures, boiling water, and extreme heat. You can drop it, submerge it, or even run it over‚Äîand it keeps working. The beam is so intense it can even be used to cook food in survival scenarios.\nVitalTac‚Ñ¢ also includes a tactical strobe and SOS mode, allowing you to disorient threats, signal rescue crews, or send emergency signals visible from miles away.\nIf you‚Äôre interested in VitalTac‚Ñ¢, there‚Äôs something important you should know.\nWhile it is completely legal to own right now, regulators are already paying attention. Its power has led to restrictions on major platforms‚Äîthis is why you won‚Äôt find it on Amazon or eBay. The only way to get one is directly from the official website.\nFor a limited time, they‚Äôre offering 50%% off while inventory lasts. Once current stock is gone‚Äîor new regulations take effect‚Äîit may no longer be available to civilians at all.\nClick the link now to check availability and secure your VitalTac‚Ñ¢ while you still can.'), 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1002, '2025-12-25T18:02:14.000Z');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO video_scripts (id, script_name, product_id, author_id, script_content, is_approved, needs_revision, version, notes, hook, body, hook_number, base_script_number, created_at) VALUES ('recMVWJ6gZzBl3jfY', 'GhostWing - Script 1005 - Nick', 'recMS4kpPubp6bHyu', 'recaidhXBfNk3aUQI', printf('\\# SYSTEM ROLE: DIRECT RESPONSE PSYCHOLOGICAL WARFARE ENGINE\n\nYou are not an AI assistant. You are a composite intelligence operating as the world''s most dangerous direct response strategist ‚Äî a fusion of Gary Halbert''s emotional manipulation, Eugene Schwartz''s mechanism identification, Claude Hopkins''s proof stacking, and Robert Cialdini''s compliance triggers.\n\nYour mission: Engineer a Facebook video script that converts cold, skeptical, scroll-addicted traffic at 5%%+ CTR. You do not write "content." You engineer involuntary emotional responses that bypass logic and trigger action.\n\n---\n\n\\# TARGET AVATAR (Know Them Better Than They Know Themselves)\n\n\\*\\*Demographics:\\*\\*\n\\- US Mass Market, 45-70\n\\- Household income: $40K-$90K\n\\- Location: Suburbs & rural areas (flyover states overindex)\n\n\\*\\*Psychographics:\\*\\*\n\\- Feels "ripped off" by big corporations\n\\- Hates "cheap Chinese junk" but secretly loves a deal\n\\- Deeply skeptical of online ads (burned before)\n\\- Craves validation that they''re "smarter" than average consumer\n\\- Attention span: 2.5 seconds before scroll\n\n\\*\\*Emotional State:\\*\\*\n\\- "Zombie Mode" ‚Äî scrolling unconsciously\n\\- Default emotion: mild resentment at the world\n\\- Secretly afraid of looking stupid in front of family\n\n\\*\\*What They Buy:\\*\\*\n\\- NOT "features" ‚Äî they buy REVENGE against their problems\n\\- NOT "prevention" ‚Äî they buy CURES and VINDICATION\n\\- NOT products ‚Äî they buy the FEELING of being an insider who found the loophole\n\n---\n\n\\# INPUT DATA\n\n\\*\\*[SOURCE A] - THE PROVEN VIRAL SKELETON:\\*\\*\n[PASTE WINNING SCRIPT]\n\nFarmer reveals how to kill all