ry street. The dark one where the family is hoping nobody tries the back door. And the one where a man with a plan lights up the whole block and every threat within two hundred yards knows ‚Äî not that house.\n\nBe that house. Tap the link below and get VitalTac while civilians can still buy one.'), 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1049, '2026-01-31T02:17:23.000Z');
