can''t buy it anywhere. It''s already banned from Amazon and eBay. The only way to get one is through the official site ‚Äî and today, they''re doing 50%% off.\nI didn''t believe the hype. Now I keep one in my truck, one by my bed, and one in my go-bag. Tap the link before it''s gone.'), 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1019, '2026-01-05T15:44:04.000Z');
