INSERT OR IGNORE INTO video_scripts (id, script_name, product_id, author_id, script_content, is_approved, needs_revision, version, notes, hook, body, hook_number, base_script_number, created_at) VALUES ('reczoM3WaJLeKBj1v', 'GhostWing - Script 1075 - Nick', 'recMS4kpPubp6bHyu', 'recaidhXBfNk3aUQI', printf('A 62-year-old grandmother in Texas flew a drone for the first time last week. One tap. That''s all it took. And the $40 billion drone industry is furious about it.\n\nHere''s the story. A single Army captain built a $99 drone so easy that people over 55 are mastering it in seconds. The big companies tried to stop him. Cease-and-desists. Retailer pressure. It hasn''t worked. Because Americans are done being told drones are "too complicated" for them.\n\nLet''s be honest about what''s really going on. The drone industry makes things complicated on purpose. Complicated means you need the $400 model. Complicated means you need the premium app. Complicated means you fly it once into a tree, shove it in a closet, and feel embarrassed. If you''ve got a $200 drone collecting dust right now, you''re not alone. Over 60%% of consumer drones get used fewer than five times. That''s not your failure. That''s their business model.\n\nAnd YouTube tutorials won''t fix it. Fifteen-minute videos from 22-year-olds who skip steps. DJI''s app looks like it was built by NASA. Your grandson means well, but he can''t be your permanent tech support. You were set up to struggle.\n\nThat''s what Captain Adam Scott decided to fix. Adam is a 44-year-old US Army officer and engineer. His team was assigned to build advanced optical equipment for a Special Forces mission in the Middle East ‚Äî capturing enemy positions from miles away without detection. After months of development, they created a breakthrough using patented MOT military optical technology. Twenty times more powerful than any commercial drone. Celebrated as the most successful military invention in recent years. Adam looked at what he built and asked one question: why should only soldiers get this? He secured every permission, redesigned it for everyday people, and called it GhostWing.\n\nHere''s what makes it different. Adam built software that boosts power and control by 120%%, then made the entire thing work with one tap. You press one button. It lifts off, stabilizes, and hovers. You''re flying. The follow-me mode films you automatically ‚Äî zero piloting skill needed. GPS locks within 900 meters and brings it home if the signal drops or battery runs low. Collision detection makes it impossible to crash. Built from carbon-polymer nanotechnology ‚Äî waterproof, indestructible, survives any temperature. Folds smaller than a water bottle. Flies 70%% quieter. Shoots full 4K that rivals cameras costing ten times more.\n\nNow picture Saturday morning. You send GhostWing over your roof ‚Äî spot those missing shingles yourself instead of paying an inspector $300. Sunday, the grandkids are playing in the yard. One tap, and GhostWing follows them capturing footage so stunning your daughter asks what camera crew you hired. Vacation next month ‚Äî sweeping aerial coastline shots that make everyone else''s photos look amateur. Property surveys. Home security at night. Everything a person over 55 actually needs a drone for, done with one tap.\n\nWhen Adam launched GhostWing, it sold out in 48 hours. The footage went viral. A 10,000-order waitlist built overnight. Now 4.9 stars across 15,000 reviews. Celebrities and filmmakers switched to it. And every single order is a vote against the companies that made drones complicated on purpose.\n\nAdam reopened orders at 50%% off ‚Äî just $99. But the last batch sold out in 48 hours at full price. At half off, this won''t last. Every order sends a message to the industry that kept drones complicated for profit. But this price is only available for the next 24 hours. Order more than one and the discounts go even deeper ‚Äî perfect gift for anyone told technology wasn''t for them. Thirty-day money-back guarantee. Zero risk. Grab yours and a few more for the people you care about before this batch is gone. Click the link below to visit the official site and order at 50%% off.'), 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1075, '2026-02-19T03:22:58.000Z');